videos.description: Luke Maye looks to be driving to the basket, but slams on the breaks and knocks down the step-back jumper.
videos.headline: Maye hits impressive step-back jumper

videos.description: Martinas Geben rises up for the offensive board and throws a laser pass to Nikola Djogo in the corner who drains the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Tough ND board leads to wide-open triple

videos.description: Notre Dame moves quickly in transition off of a defensive rebound and Rex Pflueger threads the needle with his pass to John Mooney for the assist.
videos.headline: ND's Mooney finishes great assist from Pflueger

videos.description: Nikola Djogo knocks down back-to-back 3s as Notre Dame boosts their lead in the 2nd half.
videos.headline: Djogo is on heat check from beyond the arc in 2nd half

videos.description: Luke Maye fools his defender and heads right to the basket off the screen for the wide-open jam.
videos.headline: Maye slips off the screen for wide-open dunk

videos.description: Notre Dame had one final chance to take down North Carolina and TJ Gibbs' second shot attempt hung on the rim, but fell out.
videos.headline: Notre Dame's shot to win it bounces out
